          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <ul class="featured-list">
              <li class="m-b-lg">
                <div class="featured-list-icon text-primary">
                  <span class="icon icon-lock"></span>
                </div>
                <p class="featured-list-icon-text m-b-0"><strong>Audits and assessments</strong></p>
                <p class="featured-list-icon-text">
                  Security only works when it is the default and easy.  NQIS will audit and with you, chart a course to secure technology, business practices and web presence.
                </p>
              </li>

              <li class="m-b-lg">
                <div class="featured-list-icon text-primary">
                  <span class="icon icon-add-user"></span>
                </div>
                <p class="featured-list-icon-text m-b-0"><strong>Educate </strong></p>
                <p class="featured-list-icon-text">
                  Implement industry best practices that secure other businesses - before you need them.  NQIS utilises smart, lightweight checklists and educate on how they secure each element of your digital security.
                </p>
              </li>

            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <ul class="featured-list">

              <li class="m-b-lg">
                <div class="featured-list-icon text-primary">
                  <span class="icon icon-code"></span>
                </div>
                <p class="featured-list-icon-text m-b-0"><strong>Modern security technology and research</strong></p>
                <p class="featured-list-icon-text">
                  Take advantage of the latest technologies and infosec research to provide automated and ongoing detection. Protect against the <strong>most common security threats</strong> easily and focus on what is necessary for your business.

                </p>
              </li>

              <li class="m-b-lg">
                <div class="featured-list-icon text-primary">
                  <span class="icon icon-emoji-happy"></span>
                </div>
                <p class="featured-list-icon-text m-b-0"><strong>Consulting with transparent and open dialog </strong></p>
                <p class="featured-list-icon-text">
                  Enjoy NQIS simple and clear audits.  We make digital security understandable. Create business practices knowing how they keep your business safe against threats to your information security.
                </p>
              </li>
            </ul>
